# CC PROMPT — v2.28.0 — Schema-driven ContainerCard rendering

## What this does
Replaces the hard-coded ContainerCardCollapsed/Expanded JSX in ServiceCards.jsx with
schema-driven rendering using TemplateCardRenderer + CONTAINER_SCHEMA + useCardTemplate.
This is the largest single change in the template series — read ServiceCards.jsx first.

Key changes:
- `ContainerCardCollapsed` becomes a thin wrapper around TemplateCardRenderer (collapsed phase)
- `ContainerCardExpanded` becomes a thin wrapper around TemplateCardRenderer (expanded phase)
- Tags/version state that was inside ContainerCardExpanded is lifted up to a new
  `ContainerCard` parent that manages async state and passes it to both phases
- `useCardTemplate(cardType, connectionId)` provides the effective template
- `knownLatest` and version badges now show in collapsed view
- Image name shows as `header_sub` on line 2 of collapsed card instead of in the right header
Version bump: 2.27.9 → 2.28.0

